Creating API Token in Jira
1>Open the Jira
2>Go to your profile icon
3>click on profile
4>Click on personal access token
5>Click on create token
6>Give the token name
7>click on create
8>now copy the API key

Create new request
1>Click on file on top menu bar
2>select new
3>select http
4>Now paste the URL : https://jira-jdc-t2.devtools.intel.com/browse/CAT-2
5>now click on send

How to Authorize Postman using API Key
1>Open postman
2>Click on authorization
3>Select auth type as Oauth 2.0
4>Now paste the token API key

